by Romeo Knight and Britelite


PROLOGUE
Two persons in a galaxy far far away from the Amiga, but still connected to this Universe due multi-talented passions are Britelite and Romeo Knight, alias Peter and Eike. Peter is in a band called Putrid Defecation and Eike is playing in Drown in embers. We zoom out from protracker and calibrate to their guitars. 
But we want to do this with a twist: lets find out what they know/think of each other. 

